      "Model availability depends on your subscription and what the OAuth route exposes to Wisp. Start with the default shown in Settings, then adjust only if the selected model is available on your account.": "模型可用性取决于你的订阅以及 OAuth 路线向 Wisp 暴露的内容。先使用设置中显示的默认值；只有当所选模型在你的账户中可用时再调整。",
